title: Travis Okulski
description: Travis Okulski (@tokulski) of Road and Track joins us as he makes his way through California in a glorious new Aston Martin. Matt prepares for a possible sale of his Skyline and Delorean whilst Zack and myself hurl quips of varying efficacy into the mix as usual.
author: matt@thesmokingtire.com (Matt Farah & Zack Klapman)
